{"tid":2245794,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"紅十字會輸血服務中心禁用黑色證件扣 員工斥自我審查製造白色恐怖","createTime":"2020-10-16T13:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T15:33:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"de3c9237077ba172a6cbe3796e989d199ce034c1","tid":2245794,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"黑色，已成禁忌？紅十字會輸血服務中心早前爆出有警員因不滿抽血員佩戴具抗爭意義的飾物，中止捐血活動，事後醫管局發警告，嚴禁員工執勤時穿戴任何「令人反感」飾物。消息指，近日中心再收緊禁令，以敏感為由，禁止員工使用黑色的「證件扣」，需統一改用紅色。有員工直斥白色恐怖，「黑色都唔用得，自我審查得好犀利」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，紅十字會輸血服務中心近月曾召開高層會議，討論服務質量，當中包括員工的服飾問題。據當日的會議紀錄，其中提及「專業形象及制服指引」，列明多項規定，包括「護士同事需穿着公司提供之白色Tshirt」、「將會派發統一式樣之夾連扣針，供同事佩戴名牌」及「避免不必要之配飾」等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/LFIFKIVXPNF7DIVUOYZTUCCGF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FLFIFKIVXPNF7DIVUOYZTUCCGF4%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=18ad317e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FLFIFKIVXPNF7DIVUOYZTUCCGF4%2F&h=0b7ed974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/LFIFKIVXPNF7DIVUOYZTUCCGF4/</a>"},{"pid":"19a9faf97943e84e898dd162770baca4e4c44aa7","tid":2245794,"uid":44569,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"紅十仲未識分庄閒"},{"pid":"22653c111ffc3a0df21836df40bd4bd642b12815","tid":2245794,"uid":231583,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"185e747264b8ac3584fa7ee79743a77640597cf6","tid":2245794,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19a9faf97943e84e898dd162770baca4e4c44aa7","tid":2245794,"uid":44569,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"紅十仲未識分庄閒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"